data.description: Nestled in the picturesque Village of Johnson Creek, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch style home is a true gem. The home features an open-concept layout with cathedral ceilings, creating a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen. Situated on a generously sized lot, the property has well-manicured landscaping that adds curb appeal and a welcoming vibe. While viewing, don't forget to check out the extra 0.5 space in the back of the garage along with the extra storage aisle in the basement. With its inviting curb appeal, spacious interior, and a fantastic location, it offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your own!
